---
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
---

<BlogLayout title="Historic Concerts">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Oasis: Historic Concerts</h1>

    <!-- Knebworth -->
    <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4"><a href="https://oasisreunion.live/oasis-return-to-knebworth/" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Knebworth 1996</a></h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-6">
        <div>
          <img 
            src="http://oasisreunion.live/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Oasis-Knebworth-96.jpg" 
            alt="Oasis at Knebworth"
            class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md"
          />
           <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Knebworth</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Event Details</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Dates: August 10-11, 1996</li>
            <li>Venue: Knebworth House, Hertfordshire</li>
            <li>Attendance: 250,000 (125,000 per night)</li>
            <li>Ticket Applications: 2.5 million</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Setlist</h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal pl-6">
            <li>Columbia</li>
            <li>Acquiesce</li>
            <li>Supersonic</li>
            <li>Hello</li>
            <li>Some Might Say</li>
            <li>Roll with It</li>
            <li>Slide Away</li>
            <li>Morning Glory</li>
            <li>Round Are Way</li>
            <li>Cigarettes & Alcohol</li>
            <li>Whatever</li>
            <li>Cast No Shadow</li>
            <li>Wonderwall</li>
            <li>The Masterplan</li>
            <li>Don't Look Back in Anger</li>
            <li>My Big Mouth</li>
            <li>It's Gettin' Better (Man!!)</li>
            <li>Live Forever</li>
            <li>Champagne Supernova</li>
            <li>I Am the Walrus (Beatles Cover)</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        The Knebworth concerts represent the peak of Oasis's popularity and are considered among the most significant gigs in British rock history. The band played to 250,000 people over two nights, with over 2.5 million people applying for tickets.
      </p>
    </article>

    <!-- Maine Road -->
    <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Maine Road 1996</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-6">
        <div>
          <img 
            src="http://oasisreunion.live/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Maine-Rd-1996.webp" 
            alt="Maine Road Stadium"
            class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md"
          />
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Maine Road Stadium, Manchester City's former home ground</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Event Details</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Dates: April 27-28, 1996</li>
            <li>Venue: Maine Road, Manchester</li>
            <li>Attendance: 80,000 (40,000 per night)</li>
            <li>Significance: Homecoming shows at Manchester City's stadium</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Setlist Highlights</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
            <li>Roll with It</li>
            <li>Morning Glory</li>
            <li>Wonderwall</li>
            <li>Don't Look Back in Anger</li>
            <li>Live Forever</li>
            <li>Champagne Supernova</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- Glastonbury -->
    <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Glastonbury Festival 1995</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-6">
        <div>
          <img 
            src="http://oasisreunion.live/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Oasis-Glastonbury-1995.jpg" 
            alt="Glastonbury Oasis Line up"
            class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md"
          />
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">The Pyramid Stage at Glastonbury Festival</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Event Details</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Date: June 23, 1995</li>
            <li>Venue: Worthy Farm, Pilton</li>
            <li>Attendance: 100,000+</li>
            <li>Stage: Pyramid Stage</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Notable Performances</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
            <li>Some Might Say</li>
            <li>Live Forever</li>
            <li>Cigarettes & Alcohol</li>
            <li>Supersonic</li>
            <li>Acquiesce</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- Wembley Stadium -->
    <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Wembley Stadium 2000</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-6">
        <div>
          <img 
            src="http://oasisreunion.live/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Oasis-Wembley-Stadium.jpg" 
