        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Event Details</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Dates: July 21-22, 2000</li>
            <li>Venue: Wembley Stadium, London</li>
            <li>Attendance: 125,000 (62,500 per night)</li>
            <li>Supporting Acts: Happy Mondays, Doves</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Setlist Highlights</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
            <li>Go Let It Out</li>
            <li>Who Feels Love?</li>
            <li>Supersonic</li>
            <li>Shakermaker</li>
